<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/171534-i-watched-the-movie-and-really-enjoyed-it">I watched the movie and really enjoyed it. It was very exciting and I couldn&#39;t stop watching it. I was pretty excited when I stumbled across this book. Is it similar to the movie? Is this book good? Please give me your suggestions.</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_171534'><a id="like_count_community_question_171534" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/171534?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">16 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F8908.World_War_Z">like</a></span>

